Add a Container Widget to Create Sections in the Dashboard

Use a container to group related widgets. You can apply a background color, border, and place other widgets inside it.

Drag the container widget to the dashboard canvas.
To change properties, select the widget.
Customize the appearance by setting widget properties or applying a background image.
Drag other widgets inside the container.
Increase the container size to fit more widgets.
Preview changes to the dashboard before saving.
title: Adding Containers in CRM Analytics Dashboards
